import React from 'react'
import {
  Card,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  FormErrorMessage,
  FormHelperText,
  Input
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const EarningsForm = () => {
  return(
    <Card p={2}>
      <FormControl>
        <Heading size='md' as='h2'>Earnings Form.</Heading>
        <FormLabel>Email address</FormLabel>
        <Input type='email' />
        <FormHelperText>We'll never share your email.</FormHelperText>
      </FormControl>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default EarningsForm
